\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\f0\fs36\lang9               \ul COLLEGE INFORMATION SYSTEM\ulnone\par
\b0\f1\fs22\par
\f2 College information system is a centralized approach and system for managing, storing, accessing and updating all the information and details present in relevance to students, and teaching and non-teaching faculty, increasing efficiency and convenience of information management in educational institutions\f1 .\par

\pard\sa200\sl240\slmult1\f3\u9679?\f2  Educational institutions should be able to add, edit and view student personal\par
details, like name, age, gender, email, phone number, address and so on.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  Educational institutions should be able to add, edit and view student academic\par
details, like USN, department, semester and registered courses.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  Faculty should be able to view all student personal details, and should be able\par
to view and edit internal evaluation marks and attendance of students.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  The COE office should be able to view all student details, and view and edit\par
internal and examination marks, and publish results.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  Placement section should be able to view all student details, and add\par
companies coming to the campus for placements.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  Management section should be able to view, add and edit teaching and\par
non-teaching staff details.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  Students should not be allowed to edit their personal or academic details.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  The system should be convenient and easy to use by students, management\par
and faculty.\par
\f3\u9679?\f2  The system should be a reliable source of information viewing (most\par
importantly, academic grades) for students, COE and faculty\par
